implement maxSubArray function
find the contiguous subarray which has the largest sum

there are two function:
maxSubArray function returns the sum;
maxSubArray_index function returns a tuple that includes the leftindex,rightindex,sum

example:
vector<int> vec = {1,2,3,-1,2,-3-4};
maxSubArray(vec.begin(),vec.end()) -> 7
maxSubArray_index(vec.begin(),vec,end()) -> <0,4,7>

we can use get<>() to get the value of tuple
get<0>(tuple):get the first value fo tuple


